<br>
Blessing of Ro<br>
Mana-500<br>
Cast Time-15<br>
Duration-30 min<br>
Foci- chunck of something hard to get.<br>
<br>
Spell transforms the caster into a living entity of flame. Adds 150 to attack (so we actually hit once in a while), and allows us to proc a 600pt burst of flame often.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
